title: Dead five-foot-long shark is found inside a shopping cart in a Walmart parking lot in Florida
text: Dead five-foot-long shark is found inside a shopping cart in a Walmart parking lot in Florida An assistant manager at a Florida Walmart discovered five-foot-long dead shark Police responded to store's parking lot where they found shark in shopping cart An owner of an RV parked nearby told police he heard strange noises outside And when he woke up, he found shark on the hood of his RV and placed it in cart Police said another shark was found in a resident's driveway nearby on same day Published: 17:47 GMT, 9 March 2017 | Updated: 17:55 GMT, 9 March 2017 95 shares
